entries.title: Endor System: Attenuation
entries.title_d: The Zynt'aia Spice Pirates have been increasing their activity in the Endor System. A threat to the growing research station on the local moon of Endor 2,an offensive patrol to disrupt and hopefully destroy their operations around the Declorian Territory has issued by Naval Operations.  You must survive assault by the pirates for 6 minutes to complete the operation.
